sentences: Debra "Honey" Piazza (born April 24, 1951) is an American piano player.
Piazza was born in Fairfield, California on April 24, 1951.
Her father was in the Air Force and her family moved to England for three years, when she was a child.
For the next two years she would practice extensively.
In 1972 she went to Chicago, and played with a number of blues musicians.
They got married several years later and reside in Riverside, California.
